{"tid":1562074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李桂華自爆單嘢炒咗車！？","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:12:08.000Z","uid":33939,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb7ce70505be4f777419d5847d26868b5d6d144","tid":1562074,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:08:10.000Z","msg":"如果唔知咩事，請睇最下面條link個post。<br />\n<br />\n咁我睇到fb有人comment話因為女記者問李桂華有冇問過尖沙咀開過槍嘅警員，所以李桂華先話對果個同事唔公平。<br />\n<br />\n據理力爭。我就帶住earphone再聽多次，果然01:02:20記者真係有問哩條問題(因為果刻記者問mc疊聲，所以比較難聽得清)，所以李桂華就話對果個同事唔公平。<br />\n<br />\n問題係:<br />\n1. 如果個同事話佢冇開槍射中個女仔對眼，咁跟本就唔會對佢同事唔公平。<br />\n2. 如果佢同事話有射，但唔知射中咗乜，咁都係一個事實陳述，可能個女仔周圍走導致誤射，可能眼界唔好射中。咁亦都冇話唔公平。<br />\n3. 如果佢同事話有射，而佢話係射中個女仔，咁更加唔會唔公平。<br />\n4. 最重要係記者純粹問個女仔係俾乜整傷對眼，而李桂華即刻conclude咗對佢同事唔公平，即係已經簡接認咗係佢同事打傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日冇記者會嘅真正原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1561522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1561522</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3a8662b65a9c115fdce40005c3314eafe1a77f33","tid":1562074,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2e64894b82ddf2382b63dc4152a46a25ae3ac6f1","tid":1562074,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1